NICOSIA, Cyprus -- A tornado hit Nicosia on Friday (September 18th) injuring at least 11 people. The natural phenomenon is extremely rare for the island and was accompanied by torrential rain. It caused extensive damage -- blowing away the roofs of several dozen houses, breaking windows, uprooting trees and smashing cars. (AP, Xinhua, Famagusta Gazette, Reuters - 18/09/09) 
